Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: aioquery
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: Asynchronous wrapper for source query.
Home-page: https://github.com/WardPearce/aioquery
Author: WardPearce
Author-email: wardpearce@protonmail.com
License: Apache License 2.0
Description: ## Install
        - Pypi: ``pip3 install aioquery``
        - Git: ``pip3 install git+https://github.com/WardPearce/aioquery.git``
        
        ## API
        - aioquery.client(ip, port=27015, timeout=3)
            - info(self)
            - challenge(self)
            - players(self)
        
        ### Example
        ```py
        import asyncio
        import aioquery
        
        async def testing():
            query = aioquery.client("216.52.148.47", 27015)
        
            server_info = await query.info()
            players = await query.players()
        
            print(server_info)
            print(players)
        
        loop = asyncio.get_event_loop()
        loop.run_until_complete(testing())
        ```
Platform: UNKNOWN
Requires-Python: >=3.6
